      <div type="level2">
        <head>On these materials</head>
        <p>Here are various presentations and other training resources on the use of Beta maṣāhəft website and XML encoding,
          some of which originally
          based on the training materials of <ref
            target="https://wiki.digitalclassicist.org/EpiDoc_Workshops">EpiDoc</ref>, divided into programs and single presentations. The
          programs of each workshop will use a different selection of the presentations and at a
          different moment in the life of the project. Those presentations as they were given at
          that point will be linked in the programs, or only with the participants of that specific
          training, while the latest shareable version of a given presentation is linked below. </p>
      </div>
